{"type":"message","id":"bd655f53","parentId":"6e6813e0","timestamp":"2026-04-07T15:46:59.577Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a much more comprehensive A-share quantitative research system. Let me compile a full audit report now based on what I've seen.\n","thinkingSignature":"c8b88db5692bed1f5bbcb3eedff07528719930ec62137fe41a95a336d78fd51a"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n现在我对这个 A 股量化系统有了足够了解。完整审计报告：\n\n---\n\n# A股量化系统审计报告\n\n**项目路径**: `~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/`\n\n**系统组成**:\n- 回测引擎：`backtest/` (基于 Backtrader，含 A 股 T+1/涨跌停/停牌约束)\n- 风控模块：`risk/risk_engine.py`\n- 信号系统：`signals/` (raw/merged/approved 三层结构)\n- 研究脚本：`scripts/` (150+ 脚本)\n\n---\n\n## 1️⃣ 逻辑正确性\n\n| 级别 | 问题 | 位置 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **[严重]** | **未来函数**：`y = train_data['ret_20'].shift(-5)` 用未来数据训练 | `run_ml_enhanced_backtest.py:55` |\n| **[警告]** | 动量因子使用 `fillna(method='ffill')` 已弃用 | `run_ml_enhanced_backtest.py:36` |\n| **[疑问]** | ML 模型预测结果归一化后直接加权，缺乏校准 | `run_ml_enhanced_backtest.py:66-68` |\n| **[建议]** | 建议将 `ml_score` 转为 probability 再合成 | 缺失 |\n\n✅ **良好设计**：`backtest/run_backtest.py` 正确实现了 A 股特有的 T+1/涨跌停/停牌约束\n\n---\n\n## 2️⃣ 风险隐患\n\n| 级别 | 风险 | 位置 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **[严重]** | **幸存者偏差**：未剔除退市/ST 股 | 数据加载处缺失 |\n| **[警告]** | 黑名单机制存在但未覆盖 ST/退市股 | `risk_engine.py:232` |\n| **[警告]** | 无流动性约束（ADV20）实际风控实现 | `risk_engine.py` 配置存在但未启用 |\n| **[疑问]** | 单票仓位 10% 上限，未考虑市值越小上限应越低 | `risk_engine.py` |\n\n**建议**：在 `risk_engine.py` 增加流动性加权仓位：\n```python\nif adv"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":2179,"output":1364,"cacheRead":59552,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63095,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775576772836,"responseId":"062459c568d7bf0ceccaf3cfdcb2aa4e"}}
