{"type":"message","id":"b46eb167","parentId":"6ad1a078","timestamp":"2026-04-07T15:50:06.823Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to run the audit with the claude-opus-4.6 model. Let me spawn a sub-agent to do a more thorough audit, or I can use the model directly. Looking at my available tools, I don't have a direct way to invoke a different model - I should use sessions_spawn to run this as a sub-agent with the specific model.\n","thinkingSignature":"0627806995761bc58ce0971835948ba93418743d5fc9262d96395f35658dd62a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_r3icj348lmr1_1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"agentId":"coding-agent","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system","label":"quant-audit-opus","model":"claude-opus-4.6","runtime":"subagent","task":"请对这个A股量化系统进行全面的代码审计，按以下6个维度逐一分析：\n\n1. **逻辑正确性**：信号计算、仓位管理、手续费滑点模型是否有错误？\n2. **风险隐患**：是否存在爆仓风险、未来函数、前视偏差、幸存者偏差？\n3. **代码健壮性**：异常处理、数据边界、数值稳定性（如除零）是否到位？\n4. **性能瓶颈**：回测速度慢、内存溢出的潜在热点在哪里？\n5. **过度拟合迹象**：参数敏感度、样本外测试方法是否合理？\n6. **实盘对接风险**：从回测到实盘的代码差异（如异步处理、延迟、订单未成交）是否被考虑？\n\n重点审计目录：\n- backtest/ (回测引擎)\n- risk/risk_engine.py (风控)\n- signals/ (信号流水线)\n- scripts/ (研究脚本)\n\n输出格式：\n- [严重]：致命逻辑错误，必须立即修复\n- [警告]：高概率引发失效或亏损的隐患\n- [建议]：性能优化或代码可维护性改进\n- [疑问]：需要进一步澄清设计意图的地方\n\n特别要求：\n1. 优先关注未来函数和过拟合证据\n2. 如果代码中缺失部分模块（如风控、滑点），明确指出来\n3. 最终给出0-10分的稳健性评分及理由\n\n项目路径：/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":685,"output":488,"cacheRead":61728,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62901,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775576997509,"responseId":"06245aa56d96b861bbfb615d34422ac4"}}
