{"type":"message","id":"9cb874ae","parentId":"90116193","timestamp":"2026-04-07T16:01:26.571Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All three fixes are done and committed. Let me provide a summary to the user.","thinkingSignature":"bf8ce078beaa545a5e149dbfb2a25c559a976295fe628456d016f371227a56d4"},{"type":"text","text":"三项修复全部完成并提交。\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 完成情况\n\n### 1. pct_change 零值返回 NaN\n- **文件**: `risk/exit_engine.py:74`\n- 原来：`base≤0` 时返回 `0.0`（静默失败）\n- 现在：返回 `float('nan')`，显式暴露问题\n- 测试：`math.isnan(pct_change(0, 10))` → `True`\n\n### 2. 向量化替代逐行循环\n- **文件**: `risk/exit_engine.py` 的 `load_price_snapshot()` 和 `load_latest_ma_snapshot()`\n- 原来：`for row in chunk.itertuples()` 逐行 Python 循环\n- 现在：pandas `groupby().agg()` + `idxmax()` 向量化操作，chunksize 200k→500k\n\n### 3. 订单执行模拟器\n- **新建**: `execution/simulator.py` (355行)\n- 实现了：\n  - 🚫 涨停日买入拒绝\n  - 🚫 跌停日卖出拒绝\n  - 📊 流动性约束 + 部分成交\n  - 📅 T+1 限制追踪\n  - 💰 可配置滑点（8bps买入 / 5bps卖出）\n- 测试全部通过"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed","usage":{"input":66899,"output":295,"cacheRead":19971,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":87165,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775577680240,"responseId":"06245d50648615fc5e77441111a1eed8"}}
