{"type":"message","id":"e3673e3f","parentId":"a7925e00","timestamp":"2026-04-07T16:01:48.778Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to know what else they should do to improve the overall score from 4.3/10. Let me think about the remaining issues from the audit report that haven't been fixed yet.\n\nFrom the audit:\n1. ✅ pct_change zero value → NaN (DONE)\n2. ✅ Vectorized CSV processing (DONE)\n3. ✅ Order execution simulator (DONE)\n4. Still remaining:\n   - Survivor bias: need to include delisted stocks\n   - Liquidity constraint defined but not enforced in risk_engine\n   - Configuration validation missing (no Pydantic schema)\n   - Missing parameter sensitivity analysis\n   - Blocked orders not persisted to file\n   - Broker API not integrated\n   - SMA signal logic concern (close[0] vs close[-1])\n   - Limit-up/down judgment using current bar close price\n   - Exit engine: partial exit qty rounding issue\n   - exit_engine chunk reading - still some itertuples?\n   - ML model future function concern\n   - Walkforward validation improvements\n\nI should give prioritized recommendations for the remaining items.","thinkingSignature":"c13f93eef86b792ab3d048720c17b4fe77aa2dba6bc1754d892d957cd4d225dc"},{"type":"text","text":"Based on the audit findings, here's the prioritized roadmap to improve from 4.3/10:\n\n---\n\n## 评分提升路线图\n\n### 🔴 立即处理（+1.5分）\n\n**4. 集成订单执行模拟器到风控流水线**\n- 当前 `ExecutionSimulator` 已创建，但还未接入 `risk_engine.py`\n- 需要在 `RiskEngine.apply()` 后用 simulator 重跑一次成交过滤\n- 挂单未成交 → 触发重新风控\n\n**5. 幸存者偏差 — 加入退市股数据**\n- 当前数据只包含存活股票，回测结果被高估\n- 用 `akshare` 或聚源补充退市/ST 股历史数据\n- 退市首日价格设为0，触发止损或风控\n\n**6. 流动性约束强制执行**\n- `risk_engine.py` 里 `max_order_to_adv20_ratio` 定义了但没用\n- 接入 ADV20 数据，在 `apply()` 中过滤超出流动性的信号\n\n### 🟡 高优先级处理（+2分）\n\n**7. 配置 Schema 校验**\n- 用 Pydantic 重构 `RiskConfig` 和 `ExecutionConfig`\n- 防止误配置静默生效（如 `stop_loss_pct: -999`）\n\n**8. 涨跌停判断优化**\n- `run_backtest.py:51-56` 用 `close[0]` 判断，应改用 `high[0]/low[0]`\n- 盘中用实时价判断，收盘后才能确认是否真正涨停\n\n**9. 批量订单日志持久化**\n- `blocked_orders` 统计只在内存中，需写入审计 CSV\n- 每次运行生成 `execution_audit_YYYYMMDD.csv`\n\n### 🟢 中期优化（+1.5分）\n\n**10. 参数敏感性报告**\n- 现有 `optimize_params.py` 只有网格搜索，缺敏感性分析\n- 输出参数微调 ±5% 对夏普/最大回撤的影响曲线\n\n**11. Walk-forward 验证常态化**\n- 当前有框架但不是每次必跑\n- 建议：每次策略修改必须通过 walk-forward 才能合并\n\n**12. Broker API 接入**\n- `broker_api.enabled = false` → 改为可选，配通、华泰、掘金均可\n- 打通实盘数据闭环\n\n---\n\n## 预计最终评分\n\n| 阶段 | 累计加分 | 目标评分 |\n|------|----------|----------|\n| 当前（已修复3项） | — | 4.3/10 |\n| 🔴 + 立即处理 (4-6) | +1.5 | 5.8/10 |\n| 🟡 + 高优先级 (7-9) | +2.0 | 7.8/10 |\n| 🟢 + 中期优化 (10-12) | +1.5 | **9.3/10** |\n\n---\n\n要不要现在就开始处理第4项（集成模拟器到风控流水线）？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed","usage":{"input":77,"output":854,"cacheRead":79669,"cacheWrite":7410,"totalTokens":88010,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775577689530,"responseId":"06245d597f4d319ca9df56b2a779ab9f"}}
