{"type":"message","id":"948edf5a","parentId":"0d0c031f","timestamp":"2026-04-07T16:02:49.202Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to use the minimax-m2.7 model to handle integrating the execution simulator into the risk pipeline (item 4). I should spawn a sub-agent with the specific model.","thinkingSignature":"f8f3c0c65ddfc6862dec77c9a5dc7f95e67ab7c8b7f929d29dd73f6be5be24fb"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9cyd4y2g37zp_1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"agentId":"coding-agent","model":"minimax-m2.7","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system","label":"integrate-simulator","runtime":"subagent","task":"请将已创建的 `execution/simulator.py` 集成到风控流水线中。\n\n## 任务目标\n\n修改 `risk/risk_engine.py`，在 `RiskEngine.apply()` 输出后，用 `ExecutionSimulator` 模拟成交：\n\n### 集成逻辑\n\n1. 在 `risk_engine.py` 顶部 import：\n```python\nfrom execution.simulator import ExecutionSimulator, ExecutionConfig, DailyMarketData\n```\n\n2. 在 `RiskEngine.__init__` 中初始化 `ExecutionSimulator`\n\n3. 在 `RiskEngine.apply()` 的末尾，调用 `simulator.can_buy()` / `simulator.can_sell()` 检查：\n   - 涨停日 → 拒绝买入信号\n   - 跌停日 → 拒绝卖出信号\n   - 停牌 → 拒绝信号\n\n4. 添加 `apply_execution_filter(df, market_data)` 方法：\n   - 接收 `signals` DataFrame 和 `market_data`（当日市场数据字典，key=ts_code）\n   - 返回过滤后的 DataFrame\n\n5. 在 `apply()` 方法末尾调用 `apply_execution_filter()`\n\n6. 在 `RiskContext` 中添加 `market_data: dict[str, dict]` 字段传入\n\n### 关键约束\n\n- 不要破坏现有风控逻辑，只在最后增加一层成交模拟\n- `ExecutionConfig` 默认值已考虑 A 股特性（涨停不能买、跌停不能卖）\n- 确保 `ExecutionSimulator.can_buy()` 和 `can_sell()` 签名与 `market_data` 字典匹配\n\n## 验证\n\n完成后，运行测试验证：\n```python\npython3 -c \"\nfrom risk.risk_engine import RiskEngine, RiskContext\nfrom execution.simulator import ExecutionSimulator, DailyMarketData\nprint('Import OK')\n# 简单测试\nengine = RiskEngine()\nprint('RiskEngine init OK')\nsim = ExecutionSimulator()\nprint('ExecutionSimulator init OK')\n\"\n```\n\n项目路径：`/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/qua