{"type":"message","id":"11644a79","parentId":"693e9a69","timestamp":"2026-04-07T16:14:53.130Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to continue with the remaining improvements (items 5, 10, 11, 12) and specifically wants MiniMax-M2.7 to handle this work. Let me spawn a sub-agent with MiniMax-M2.7 to tackle these remaining items:\n\n1. Item 5: Survivor bias - add delisted stock data\n2. Item 10: Parameter sensitivity analysis\n3. Item 11: Walk-forward validation as mandatory gate\n4. Item 12: Broker API integration\n\nThese are more complex tasks. Let me spawn a sub-agent.","thinkingSignature":"5788f421ae3c57a96fc698b8a5714edef1bc21feeddc8538d053ff8751bdc9ed"},{"type":"text","text":"好，让 MiniMax-M2.7 一次性处理剩余4项。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_tc2td18n3lng_1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"agentId":"coding-agent","model":"minimax-m2.7","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system","label":"audit-round3-m27","runtime":"subagent","task":"请处理量化系统审计报告中的剩余4项优化。逐项实施，每完成一项验证一项。\n\n## 项目路径\n`/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system`\n\n## 待处理项\n\n### 项5: 退市股数据处理（解决幸存者偏差）\n**目标**：回测数据中包含退市/ST股，避免高估收益。\n\n**实现方案**：\n在 `risk/risk_engine.py` 中添加 `RiskConfig` 字段：\n```python\nadd delisted_stocks: bool = True\n```\n在 `apply()` 中，黑名单过滤前增加：\n```python\n# 加载退市/ST股列表（从本地CSV）\nDELISTED_CODES_PATH = Path(\"data/delisted_stocks.csv\")  # 包含 ts_code, delist_date 字段\n```\n如果 `config.add_delisted_stocks` 为 True，则把退市股加入 `blocked_codes`，或在信号过滤时剔除。\n\n同时在 `risk/rules/` 目录创建 `delisted_filter.py`：\n- 读取退市股数据\n- 如果信号 `ts_code` 在退市列表且 `trade_date >= delist_date`，则拒绝\n- 对 ST 股（同上处理）\n\n**验证**：\n```python\npython3 -c \"\nfrom risk.rules.delisted_filter import DelistedFilter\nf = DelistedFilter()\n# 测试\n\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### 项10: 参数敏感性分析报告\n**目标**：输出参数微调±5%对结果影响的分析报告。\n\n在 `scripts/` 下创建 `sensitivity_analysis.py`：\n```python\n#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"参数敏感性分析 - 扫描关键参数±5%区间对策略指标的影响\"\"\"\n\nimport argparse\nimport json\nfrom pathlib import Path\nimport numpy as np\nimport pandas as pd\n\nPROJECT_ROOT = Path(__file__).resolve().parents[1]\nSCRIPTS_DIR = PROJECT_ROOT / \"scripts\"\nif str(SCRIPTS_DIR) not in sys.path:\n    sys.path.insert(0, str(SCRIPTS_DIR))\n\n\ndef run_sensitivity_analysis(\n    base_config: dict,\n    param_ranges: dict[str, tuple[float, float, int]],  # name -> (min, max, steps)\n    metric: str = \"sharpe_ratio\",  # 或 \"max_drawdown\", \"total_return\"\n) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"\n    对 base_config 中的每个参数，在 min-max 区间内均匀采样，\n    运行回测，记录 metric 值，返回敏感性报告。\n    \"\"\"\n    results = []\n    for param_name, (p_min, p_max, steps) in param_ranges.items():\n        for i, val in enumerate(np.linspace(p_min, p_max, steps)):\n            cfg = {**base_config, param_name: val}\n            # TODO: 调用回测或读取已有的回测结果\n            # metric_val = run_backtest_with_config(cfg)[metric]\n            metric_val = 0.0  # placeholder\n            results.append({\n                \"param\": param_name,\n                \"param_value\": round(val, 4),\n                \"metric_value\": metric_val,\n            })\n    \n    # 生成报告\n    report = {\"param_sensitivity\": []}\n    for param_name in param_ranges:\n        param_results = [r for r in results if r[\"param\"] == param_name]\n        values = [r[\"param_value\"] for r in param_results]\n        metrics = [r[\"metric_value\"] for r in param_results]\n        # 计算敏感性指标\n        max_metric = max(metrics)\n        min_metric = min(metrics)\n        sensitivity = max_metric - min_metric if max_metric != min_metric else 0.0\n        stable = sensitivity < 0.05  # 敏感性 < 5% 认为稳定\n        report[\"param_sensitivity\"].append({\n            \"param\": param_name,\n            \"sensitivity\": round(sensitivity, 4),\n            \"stable\": stable,\n            \"best_value\": values[metrics.index(max_metric)],\n            \"worst_value\": values[metrics.index(min_metric)],\n            \"detail\": [{\"value\": v, \"metric\": m} for v, m in zip(values, metrics)],\n        })\n    \n    return report\n```\n\n在 `scripts/` 下创建 `run_sensitivity.py`，读取已有回测结果 JSON 文件进行敏感性分析。\n\n**验证**：确保脚本能运行（可以无数据运行验证逻辑）\n```bash\npython3 scripts/sensitivity_analysis.py --help\n```\n\n---\n\n### 项11: Walk-forward 验证强制化\n**目标**：每次策略参数修改必须通过 walk-forward 才能合并。\n\n在 `scripts/` 下创建 `wf_gate.py`：\n```python\n#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"Walk-forward gate: 策略上线前必须通过 walk-forward 验证。\n\n检查项：\n1. train/valid/test 窗口不重叠\n2. OOS Sharpe > 0\n3. OOS 最大回撤 < 阈值\n4. OOS 与 IS 性能衰减 < 50%\n\"\"\"\n\nimport json\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nWF_RESULT_PATH = Path(\"backtest/results/walkforward/\")\n\ndef check_wf_gate(wf_result_file: str, config: dict) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"检查 walk-forward 结果是否通过 gate。\"\"\"\n    with open(wf_result_file) as f:\n        wf = json.load(f)\n    \n    checks = {}\n    all_passed = True\n    \n    # Check 1: OOS Sharpe > 0\n    oos_sharpe = wf.get(\"oos_sharpe\", -999)\n    checks[\"oos_sharpe_positive\"] = oos_sharpe > 0\n    if not checks[\"oos_sharpe_positive\"]:\n        all_passed = False\n    \n    # Check 2: OOS max drawdown < threshold\n    oos_max_dd = wf.get(\"oos_max_drawdown\", 999)\n    max_dd_th = config.get(\"max_drawdown_threshold\", 0.15)\n    checks[\"oos_max_drawdown_ok\"] = abs(oos_max_dd) < max_dd_th\n    if not checks[\"oos_max_drawdown_ok\"]:\n        all_passed = False\n    \n    # Check 3: IS/OOS performance degradation < 50%\n    is_return = wf.get(\"is_annual_return\", 0)\n    oos_return = wf.get(\"oos_annual_return\", 0)\n    if is_return > 0:\n        degradation = (is_return - oos_return) / is_return\n    else:\n        degradation = 1.0\n    checks[\"degradation_ok\"] = degradation < 0.5\n    if not checks[\"degradation_ok\"]:\n        all_passed = False\n    \n    return {\"passed\": all_passed, \"checks\": checks, \"details\": wf}\n```\n\n**验证**：\n```bash\npython3 scripts/wf_gate.py --help\n```\n\n---\n\n### 项12: Broker API 基础框架\n**目标**：建立 Broker API 接入框架，支持通投/华泰/掘金。\n\n在 `execution/` 下创建 `broker_base.py`：\n```python\n\"\"\"Broker API base class and adapter registry.\"\"\"\n\nfrom abc import ABC, abstractmethod\nfrom dataclasses import dataclass\nfrom typing import Optional\n\n@dataclass\nclass OrderResult:\n    order_id: str\n    status: str  # submitted / filled / rejected / cancelled\n    filled_qty: int\n    filled_price: float\n    message: str = \"\"\n\nclass BrokerAdapter(ABC):\n    @abstractmethod\n    def submit_order(self, ts_code: str, side: str, qty: int, price: float) -> OrderResult:\n        pass\n    \n    @abstractmethod\n    def query_position(self, ts_code: str) -> dict:\n        pass\n    \n    @abstractmethod\n    def query_account(self) -> dict:\n        pass\n\n# 适配器注册表\n_BROKER_REGISTRY: dict[str, type[BrokerAdapter]] = {}\n\ndef register_broker(name: str):\n    def deco(cls):\n        _BROKER_REGISTRY[name] = cls\n        return cls\n    return deco\n\ndef get_broker(name: str, **kwargs) -> BrokerAdapter:\n    if name not in _BROKER_REGISTRY:\n        raise ValueError(f\"Unknown broker: {name}. Available: {list(_BROKER_REGISTRY.keys())}\")\n    return _BROKER_REGISTRY[name](**kwargs)\n```\n\n创建 `execution/broker_simulated.py`：\n- 实现模拟券商（用于 paper trading）\n- 所有订单直接成交，无延迟\n\n创建 `execution/broker_tongdaxin.py`：\n- 占位实现：注释说明同花顺 API 接入方式\n- 抛出 `NotImplementedError`\n\n更新 `config/live_trading_v1.json`：\n- 替换 `\"enabled\": false` 为 broker 配置示例\n\n**验证**：\n```python\npython3 -c \"\nfrom execution.broker_base import get_broker, register_broker\nfrom execution.broker_simulated import SimulatedBroker\nbroker = get_broker('simulated')\nprint('Broker:', broker)\nresult = broker.submit_order('000001.SZ', 'BUY', 100, 10.0)\nprint('Order:', result)\n\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## 提交\n\n每完成一项后验证，然后：\n```bash\ngit add <changed files>\ngit commit -m \"<description>\"\n```\n\n完成后汇总所有改动。\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed","usage":{"input":77,"output":2198,"cacheRead":19971,"cacheWrite":88856,"totalTokens":111102,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775578459095,"responseId":"0624605b420c622e7fc2dfa5a876995d"}}
