{"type":"message","id":"2c6552cc","parentId":"dba85902","timestamp":"2026-04-07T16:30:09.545Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to continue with:\n1. Broker 真实API接入（同花顺/华泰已预留占位，需填入真实接口）\n2. Walk-forward 常态化CI/CD（wf_gate 已有，需集成到 git hook）\n\nLet me spawn MiniMax-M2.7 to handle these two tasks.","thinkingSignature":"abaf5b8e0036616da094a5a165bef471d156d21ea8382036244084e4447e238c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_nloi56026q8i_1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"agentId":"coding-agent","model":"minimax-m2.7","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system","label":"broker-api-plus-cicd","runtime":"subagent","task":"请处理两个任务：Broker 真实API接入 + Walk-forward CI/CD 集成。\n\n## 项目路径\n`/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system`\n\n---\n\n## 任务一：Broker 真实API接入\n\n### 目标\n完善 `execution/broker_tongdaxin.py`，填入真实同花顺接口逻辑（基于 requests HTTP 调用）。\n\n### 同花顺API分析\n同花顺个人数据接口（投资账本 tzzb.10jqka.com.cn）通常使用以下方式：\n1. 登录获取 session cookie\n2. 持仓查询接口\n3. 下单接口\n\n**重要**：同花顺官方未开放 API，需通过以下方式：\n- 方法A：`akshare` 库获取行情/财务数据（非交易）\n- 方法B：同花顺 iFinD 接口（付费）\n- 方法C：通过 `ths_local_holdings` skill 获取持仓（网页抓取）\n\n**实际可行方案**：\n由于交易API未开放，采用**数据整合方案**：\n1. 保留 `TongdaxinBroker` 架构\n2. 在 `broker_tongdaxin.py` 中实现：\n   - `query_position()`: 调用 `akshare` 获取持仓（如有）或读取本地持仓文件\n   - `query_account()`: 读取账户资金文件\n   - `submit_order()`: **不实现真实下单**，而是将订单写入 `orders/proposed/` 目录作为人工确认队列\n   - 注释说明：真实下单需要券商 API（如中信/华泰证券 API），此处为人工确认队列模式\n\n```python\n# 在 submit_order() 中\ndef submit_order(self, ts_code: str, side: str, qty: int, price: float) -> OrderResult:\n    # 同花顺官方未开放交易API，将订单写入人工确认队列\n    order_record = {\n        \"order_id\": f\"TDX_{datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d%H%M%S')}\",\n        \"ts_code\": ts_code,\n        \"side\": side,\n        \"qty\": qty,\n        \"price\": price,\n        \"status\": \"pending_manual\",\n        \"created_at\": datetime.now().isoformat(),\n    }\n    orders_dir = Path(\"orders/manual_confirm\")\n    orders_dir.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n    order_file = orders_dir / f\"{order_record['order_id']}.json\"\n    order_file.write_text(json.dumps(order_record, ensure_ascii=False))\n    return OrderResult(\n        order_id=order_record[\"order_id\"],\n        status=\"pending_manual\",\n        filled_qty=0,\n        filled_price=0.0,\n        message=\"同花顺API未开放交易，此订单已写入人工确认队列\"\n    )\n```\n\n3. 更新 `config/live_trading_v1.json` 中的 broker_api 配置，添加 `manual_confirm_queue` 选项\n\n---\n\n### 同时创建一个 `broker_xtquant.py`（迅投极速交易接口）\n迅投 QMT 是许多券商使用的量化交易接口（如华泰、招商等）：\n\n```python\n# execution/broker_xtquant.py\n\"\"\"迅投 QMT 量化交易接口适配器\n\nQMT 接口规范：\n- xtquant 库：pip install xtquant\n- 接口：xtquant.mk.module(MktStockPy)\n- 登录：xtquant.xtdatacenter.start()\n\"\"\"\nimport json\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom execution.broker_base import BrokerAdapter, OrderResult\n\nclass XtQuantBroker(BrokerAdapter):\n    \"\"\"迅投 QMT 适配器（适用于华泰、招商等使用迅投系统的券商）\"\"\"\n    \n    def __init__(self, account: str, password: str, com_server: str = \"\"):\n        # account: 资金账号\n        # password: 交易密码\n        # com_server: 券商通讯服务器地址\n        self.account = account\n        self.password = password\n        self.com_server = com_server\n        self._connected = False\n        self._position_cache = {}\n    \n    def connect(self):\n        \"\"\"连接迅投交易服务器\"\"\"\n        try:\n            import xtquant\n            # xtquant.xtdatacenter.start(self.com_server, self.account, self.password)\n            self._connected = True\n        except ImportError:\n            raise RuntimeError(\"请先安装 xtquant: pip install xtquant\")\n        except Exception as e:\n            raise RuntimeError(f\"迅投连接失败: {e}\")\n    \n    def submit_order(self, ts_code: str, side: str, qty: int, price: float) -> OrderResult:\n        if not self._connected:\n            return OrderResult(order_id=\"\", status=\"error\", filled_qty=0, filled_price=0.0,\n                             message=\"未连接\")\n        try:\n            import xtquant\n            mkt = xtquant.mk.module(\"MktStockPy\")\n            # 下单...\n            return OrderResult(...)\n        except NotImplementedError:\n            # 占位：真实 QMT 下单实现\n            return OrderResult(order_id=\"\", status=\"pending\", filled_qty=0, filled_price=0.0,\n                             message=\"QMT下单占位，需填写真实account和com_server\")\n    \n    def query_position(self, ts_code: str) -> dict:\n        # ...\n    \n    def query_account(self) -> dict:\n        # ...\n```\n\n---\n\n## 任务二：Walk-forward CI/CD 集成\n\n### 目标\n将 `wf_gate.py` 集成到 git hook，实现策略上线前自动检查。\n\n### 步骤\n\n1. 在 `scripts/` 下创建 `setup_git_hooks.py`：\n```python\n#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"Install git pre-commit hooks for strategy validation.\"\"\"\n\nHOOK_CONTENT = '''#!/bin/bash\n# Pre-commit hook: run walk-forward gate before allowing strategy file commits\n\necho \"🔍 Running walk-forward validation gate...\"\n\nSTRATEGY_FILES=$(git diff --cached --name-only | grep -E \"config/(live_trading|strategy)\")\n\nif [ -z \"$STRATEGY_FILES\" ]; then\n    echo \"✅ No strategy files changed, skipping WF gate.\"\n    exit 0\nfi\n\n# Check for wf result\nWF_RESULT=\"backtest/results/wf_latest.json\"\nif [ ! -f \"$WF_RESULT\" ]; then\n    echo \"❌ No walk-forward result found at $WF_RESULT\"\n    echo \"   Please run: python3 scripts/run_walk_forward.py\"\n    exit 1\nfi\n\nRESULT=$(python3 scripts/wf_gate.py --wf-result \"$WF_RESULT\" --json 2>&1)\necho \"$RESULT\"\n\nPASSED=$(echo \"$RESULT\" | python3 -c \"import sys,json; print(json.load(sys.stdin).get('passed', False))\")\nif [ \"$PASSED\" != \"True\" ]; then\n    echo \"❌ Walk-forward gate FAILED. Commit blocked.\"\n    echo \"   Fix the issues or use --no-verify to bypass (not recommended).\"\n    exit 1\nfi\n\necho \"✅ Walk-forward gate PASSED.\"\nexit 0\n'''\n```\n\n2. 在项目根目录安装 hook：\n```bash\n# 在 setup_git_hooks.py 中实现\ngit_hooks_dir = Path(\".git/hooks\")\nhook_file = git_hooks_dir / \"pre-commit\"\nhook_file.write_text(HOOK_CONTENT)\nhook_file.chmod(0o755)\n```\n\n3. 在 `scripts/` 下创建 `run_walk_forward.py`（简单的 walk-forward 触发脚本）\n\n4. 更新 README.md 添加 CI/CD 说明\n\n### 验证\n```bash\npython3 scripts/setup_git_hooks.py\n# 确认 .git/hooks/pre-commit 已创建\ncat .git/hooks/pre-commit | head -5\n```\n\n---\n\n## 提交规范\n每完成一项验证后单独提交：\n```bash\ngit add <files>\ngit commit -m \"<description>\"\n```\n\n完成后汇总所有改动。\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed","usage":{"input":77,"output":1848,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":112528,"totalTokens":114453,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775579374662,"responseId":"062463ee7f38ea53878319cd6363a477"}}
