{"type":"message","id":"e7004185","parentId":"8faea09e","timestamp":"2026-04-07T16:31:14.662Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b52675a2b4ca0c2ca82e51906db7\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"sender\": \"张玲\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-04-08 00:31 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"name\": \"张玲\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b52675a2b4ca0c2ca82e51906db7]\n张玲: 退市股数据源（data/delisted_stocks.csv 需要真实数据填充）这个也需要处理"}],"timestamp":1775579474656}}
{"type":"message","id":"67e6401d","parentId":"e7004185","timestamp":"2026-04-07T16:31:38.557Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to also handle the delisted stocks data source. This was item 5's remaining part - actually filling in the data. Let me spawn another subagent to handle this specific task.","thinkingSignature":"a43d6bc30960081b2027ef8aeca70b5a49021a87edd004976173a95319d73baf"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ch0rg5md9p2y_1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"agentId":"coding-agent","model":"minimax-m2.7","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system","label":"delisted-data-source","runtime":"subagent","task":"请处理退市股数据源的获取和填充。\n\n## 项目路径\n`/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system`\n\n## 任务目标\n生成 `data/delisted_stocks.csv`，包含A股历史退市/ST股数据。\n\n## 实现方案\n\n### 方案1：使用 akshare 获取历史退市数据\n在 `scripts/` 下创建 `fetch_delisted_stocks.py`：\n\n```python\n#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"获取A股历史退市/ST股数据，输出到 data/delisted_stocks.csv\n\n数据源：akshare\n- akshare.stock_delist() - 退市股票\n- akshare.stock_st() - ST股列表\n\n输出格式：\nts_code, delist_date, delist_reason, is_st, st_date, remove_date\n000001.XSHE, 20201231, 退市, False, ,\n600001.XSHE, , , True, 20200101, 20201231\n\"\"\"\n\nimport akshare as ak\nimport pandas as pd\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\ndef fetch_delisted_stocks(output_path: str = \"data/delisted_stocks.csv\") -> pd.DataFrame:\n    \"\"\"获取并保存退市/ST股数据\"\"\"\n    \n    records = []\n    \n    # 1. 获取退市股票\n    print(\"Fetching delisted stocks from akshare...\")\n    try:\n        df_delist = ak.stock_delist()\n        print(f\"  Got {len(df_delist)} delisted records\")\n        # 规范化列名\n        if \"股票代码\" in df_delist.columns:\n            df_delist = df_delist.rename(columns={\n                \"股票代码\": \"ts_code\",\n                \"退市日期\": \"delist_date\",\n                \"退市原因\": \"delist_reason\",\n            })\n        for _, row in df_delist.iterrows():\n            records.append({\n                \"ts_code\": row.get(\"ts_code\", \"\"),\n                \"delist_date\": row.get(\"delist_date\", \"\"),\n                \"delist_reason\": row.get(\"delist_reason\", \"\"),\n                \"is_st\": False,\n                \"st_date\": \"\",\n                \"remove_date\": \"\",\n            })\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"  Failed to fetch delisted stocks: {e}\")\n    \n    # 2. 获取ST股（当前ST列表）\n    print(\"Fetching current ST stocks...\")\n    try:\n        df_st = ak.stock_st()\n        print(f\"  Got {len(df_st)} ST records\")\n        for _, row in df_st.iterrows():\n            records.append({\n                \"ts_code\": row.get(\"ts_code\", \"\"),\n                \"delist_date\": \"\",\n                \"delist_reason\": \"\",\n                \"is_st\": True,\n                \"st_date\": datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\"),\n                \"remove_date\": \"\",\n            })\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"  Failed to fetch ST stocks: {e}\")\n    \n    if not records:\n        print(\"No records fetched, creating empty file.\")\n        df = pd.DataFrame(columns=[\n            \"ts_code\", \"delist_date\", \"delist_reason\", \"is_st\", \"st_date\", \"remove_date\"\n        ])\n    else:\n        df = pd.DataFrame(records)\n        # 规范化 ts_code 格式（转为 000001.SZ 格式）\n        df[\"ts_code\"] = df[\"ts_code\"].apply(normalize_ts_code)\n    \n    # 保存\n    output_path = Path(output_path)\n    output_path.parent.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n    df.to_csv(output_path, index=False, encoding=\"utf-8\")\n    print(f\"Saved {len(df)} records to {output_path}\")\n    return df\n\ndef normalize_ts_code(code: str) -> str:\n    \"\"\"将 600001 转为 600001.SH 格式\"\"\"\n    code = str(code).strip()\n    if not code:\n        return \"\"\n    if \".\" in code:\n        return code\n    if code.startswith((\"600\", \"601\", \"603\", \"605\", \"688\")):\n        return f\"{code}.SH\"\n    if code.startswith((\"000\", \"001\", \"002\", \"003\", \"300\", \"301\")):\n        return f\"{code}.SZ\"\n    return code\n\ndef main():\n    import argparse\n    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser(description=\"获取A股退市/ST股数据\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--output\", default=\"data/delisted_stocks.csv\")\n    args = parser.parse_args()\n    fetch_delisted_stocks(args.output)\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()\n```\n\n### 方案2：如果 akshare 不可用，创建带注释的空模板\n\n如果运行 `fetch_delisted_stocks.py` 时 akshare 不可用或网络问题，自动降级：\n\n```python\n# 降级：创建模板文件，说明如何手动填充\noutput_path = Path(\"data/delisted_stocks.csv\")\noutput_path.parent.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\ntemplate = \"\"\"ts_code,delist_date,delist_reason,is_st,st_date,remove_date\n# 请运行: pip install akshare && python3 scripts/fetch_delisted_stocks.py\n# 或手动从以下来源补充：\n# 1. 同花顺问财：http://www.10jqka.com.cn/\n# 2. 聚宽：https://www.joinquant.com/\n# 3. Tushare：http://www.tushare.pro/\n\"\"\"\noutput_path.write_text(template, encoding=\"utf-8\")\n```\n\n### 验证\n```bash\n# 先检查 akshare 是否可用\npython3 -c \"import akshare; print(akshare.__version__)\"\n\n# 运行数据获取脚本\npython3 scripts/fetch_delisted_stocks.py\n\n# 检查输出\nhead data/delisted_stocks.csv\nwc -l data/delisted_stocks.csv\n```\n\n### 额外：创建定时更新脚本\n在 `scripts/` 下创建 `update_delisted_data.sh`：\n```bash\n#!/bin/bash\n# 每周一早上9点更新退市股数据\n0 9 * * 1 cd $(git rev-parse --show-toplevel) && python3 scripts/fetch_delisted_stocks.py >> logs/delisted_update.log 2>&1\n```\n\n## 提交\n```bash\ngit add scripts/fetch_delisted_stocks.py data/delisted_stocks.csv\ngit commit -m \"add: delisted stocks data fetcher using akshare\"\n```\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed","usage":{"input":77,"output":1515,"cacheRead":112335,"cacheWrite":2483,"totalTokens":116410,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775579474667,"responseId":"062464535d6fc04c41e8412970ed5ee2"}}
