{"type":"message","id":"a8de4b43","parentId":"9bee315f","timestamp":"2026-04-07T16:42:10.440Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There's one remaining bottleneck - the `df.apply(_max_qty, axis=1)` in `_apply_liquidity_filter`. Let me also check the execution filter for any remaining row-by-row operations.","thinkingSignature":"332175378560c58a1d228aa68342af77bc71750823300d6f64f9638a3c6c9d19"},{"type":"text","text":"还有1处：`df.apply(..., axis=1)` 是性能杀手。另外 `apply_execution_filter` 内部也还有逐行循环。一并修了：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gl3fej1utazi_1","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":100,"offset":378,"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/risk/risk_engine.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed","usage":{"input":103832,"output":144,"cacheRead":19971,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":123947,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775580126636,"responseId":"062466de04211d509ca0d3f1275f1247"}}
{"type":"message","id":"01d07fd4","parentId":"a8de4b43","timestamp":"2026-04-07T16:42:10.486Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_gl3fej1utazi_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"            df[\"approved\"] = False\n            if \"target_weight\" in df.columns:\n                df[\"target_weight\"] = 0.0\n            return df\n\n        if decision.risk_off:\n            df[\"risk_status\"] = \"riskoff\"\n            df[\"approved\"] = df[\"signal_type\"].isin(self.SELL_SIGNAL_TYPES)\n            buy_mask = df[\"signal_type\"].isin(self.BUY_SIGNAL_TYPES)\n            if self.config.allow_new_buy_when_riskoff:\n                df.loc[buy_mask, \"approved\"] = True\n                self._append_adjustment(df, buy_mask, \"riskoff_buy_limited\")\n            else:\n                df.loc[buy_mask, \"approved\"] = False\n                self._append_adjustment(df, buy_mask, \"riskoff_block_buy\")\n                if \"target_weight\" in df.columns:\n                    df.loc[buy_mask, \"target_weight\"] = 0.0\n\n            return self._apply_weight_caps(df, exposure_cap=self.config.riskoff_total_exposure)\n\n        # 3) 正常态：先标记通过，后续补充细化约束\n        df[\"risk_status\"] = \"normal\"\n        df[\"approved\"] = True\n        df = self._apply_weight_caps(df, exposure_cap=self.config.max_total_exposure)\n\n        # 5) 流动性约束\n        df = self._apply_liquidity_filter(df, context.market_data, context.trade_date)\n\n        # 6) 成交模拟过滤（涨跌停/停牌）\n        df = self.apply_execution_filter(df, context.market_data, context.trade_date)\n\n        return df\n\n    def _apply_liquidity_filter(\n        self,\n        df: pd.DataFrame,\n        market_data: dict[str, dict],\n        trade_date: str,\n    ) -> pd.DataFrame:\n        \"\"\"Vectorized liquidity check: cap order size to ADV20 * ratio.\n\n        Only applies to BUY signals when config.enforce_liquidity is True.\n        \"\"\"\n        if df is None or df.empty:\n            return df\n        if not self.config.enforce_liquidity or not market_data:\n            return df\n\n        buy_mask = df[\"signal_type\"].isin(self.BUY_SIGNAL_TYPES) & df[\"approved\"].fillna(False)\n        if not buy_mask.any():\n            return df\n\n        # Build ADV20 lookup\n        adv_map = {\n            code: (md.get(\"adv20\", 0.0) or 0.0)\n            for code, md in market_data.items()\n        }\n\n        # Vectorized: compute max_qty per signal\n        def _max_qty(row) -> int:\n            if row[\"ts_code\"] not in adv_map:\n                return int(1e9)  # no data → allow\n            adv = adv_map[row[\"ts_code\"]]\n            if adv <= 0:\n                return int(1e9)\n            price = row.get(\"price\", 0.0)\n            if price <= 0:\n                price = 1.0\n            return max(1, int(adv * self.config.max_order_to_adv20_ratio / price))\n\n        df[\"_max_qty_by_adv\"] = df.apply(_max_qty, axis=1)\n\n        # Adjust target_weight if order exceeds liquidity\n        if \"target_weight\" in df.columns:\n            nav = df.get(\"account_nav\", pd.Series([None] * len(df)))\n            total_nav = nav.iloc[0] if not nav.empty and nav.iloc[0] else 1.0\n            weight_map = df[\"target_weight\"] * total_nav / df[\"price\"].replace(0, 1.0)\n            excess = weight_map > df[\"_max_qty_by_adv\"]\n            if excess.any():\n                excess_mask = buy_mask & excess\n                df.loc[excess_mask, \"risk_adjustment\"] = (\n                    df.loc[excess_mask, \"risk_adjustment\"].str.replace(\"none\", \"\", regex=False)\n                    + \"|liquidity_capped\"\n                )\n                _append_audit(\n                    trade_date,\n                    \";\".join(df.loc[excess_mask, \"ts_code\"].tolist()),\n                    \"BUY\",\n                    \"LIQUIDITY_CAPPED\",\n                    f\"qty > ADV20 * {self.config.max_order_to_adv20_ratio:.2%}\",\n                )\n\n        df.drop(columns=[\"_max_qty_by_adv\"], inplace=True, errors=\"ignore\")\n        return df\n\n    def apply_execution_filter(self, signals: pd.DataFrame, market_data: dict[str, dict], trade_date: str = \"\") -> pd.DataFrame:\n        \"\"\"Vectorized execution filter:涨跌停/停牌 + 流动性。\n\n        Args:\n            signals: 通过风控的信号 DataFrame\n\n[100 more lines in file. Use offset=478 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775580130478}}
{"type":"message","id":"2132650c","parentId":"01d07fd4","timestamp":"2026-04-07T16:42:18.547Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the bottlenecks clearly:\n\n1. `_apply_liquidity_filter`: uses `df.apply(_max_qty, axis=1)` which is O(N) Python loop\n2. `apply_execution_filter`: also has row-by-row iteration\n\nLet me rewrite both methods to be fully vectorized.\n\nFor `_apply_liquidity_filter`:\n- Replace `apply(_max_qty, axis=1)` with vectorized pandas operations\n- Create a ts_code → adv mapping, then map to the dataframe\n\nFor `apply_execution_filter`:\n- Replace the `for idx in df.index[buy_mask]` loop with vectorized operations\n\n\n- Build a market data lookup for ts_codes, then use vectorized boolean indexing to filter both buy and sell signals at once","thinkingSignature":"28da5e4e8c83a34d3db32be27928439e6f0e27387815c871e6cf37dc322e4d97"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_orxnuyal4lre_1","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":100,"offset":478,"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/risk/risk_engine.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed","usage":{"input":105004,"output":230,"cacheRead":19971,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":125205,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775580130489,"responseId":"062466e23504800b7eb6266c4b94899a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f5e83212","parentId":"2132650c","timestamp":"2026-04-07T16:42:18.592Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_orxnuyal4lre_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"            market_data: 当日市场数据字典\n            trade_date: 审计日志用\n        \"\"\"\n        if signals is None or signals.empty:\n            return signals\n        if not market_data:\n            return signals\n\n        df = signals.copy()\n        df[\"execution_rejected\"] = False\n        df[\"execution_reject_reason\"] = \"\"\n\n        # Build DailyMarketData dict once\n        md_dict: dict[str, DailyMarketData] = {}\n        for code, md in market_data.items():\n            md_dict[code] = DailyMarketData(\n                ts_code=md.get(\"ts_code\", code),\n                trade_date=md.get(\"trade_date\", 0),\n                open=md.get(\"open\", 0.0),\n                high=md.get(\"high\", 0.0),\n                low=md.get(\"low\", 0.0),\n                close=md.get(\"close\", 0.0),\n                limit_up=md.get(\"limit_up\", 0.0),\n                limit_down=md.get(\"limit_down\", 0.0),\n                suspended=bool(md.get(\"suspended\", False)),\n                adv20=md.get(\"adv20\", 0.0),\n            )\n\n        # Vectorized mask operations\n        codes = df[\"ts_code\"].map(lambda x: x in md_dict)\n        buy_mask = df[\"signal_type\"].isin(self.BUY_SIGNAL_TYPES) & codes\n        sell_mask = df[\"signal_type\"].isin(self.SELL_SIGNAL_TYPES) & codes\n\n        # BUY: check can_buy\n        if buy_mask.any():\n            buy_rejected = pd.Series(False, index=df.index)\n            buy_reasons = pd.Series(\"\", index=df.index)\n            for idx in df.index[buy_mask]:\n                row = df.loc[idx]\n                mkt = md_dict.get(row[\"ts_code\"])\n                if mkt:\n                    ok, reason = self._simulator.can_buy(mkt)\n                    if not ok:\n                        buy_rejected[idx] = True\n                        buy_reasons[idx] = f\"买入拒绝({reason})\"\n            rejected_buy = buy_rejected[buy_rejected]\n            if rejected_buy.any():\n                df.loc[rejected_buy.index, \"execution_rejected\"] = True\n                df.loc[rejected_buy.index, \"execution_reject_reason\"] = buy_reasons.loc[rejected_buy.index]\n                df.loc[rejected_buy.index, \"approved\"] = False\n                df.loc[rejected_buy.index, \"risk_adjustment\"] = (\n                    df.loc[rejected_buy.index, \"risk_adjustment\"].str.replace(\"none\", \"\", regex=False) + \"|exec_blocked\"\n                )\n                if \"target_weight\" in df.columns:\n                    df.loc[rejected_buy.index, \"target_weight\"] = 0.0\n                for _idx in rejected_buy.index:\n                    _append_audit(\n                        trade_date,\n                        df.loc[_idx, \"ts_code\"],\n                        df.loc[_idx, \"signal_type\"],\n                        \"REJECTED\",\n                        buy_reasons.loc[_idx],\n                    )\n\n        # SELL: check can_sell\n        if sell_mask.any():\n            sell_rejected = pd.Series(False, index=df.index)\n            sell_reasons = pd.Series(\"\", index=df.index)\n            for idx in df.index[sell_mask]:\n                row = df.loc[idx]\n                mkt = md_dict.get(row[\"ts_code\"])\n                if mkt:\n                    ok, reason = self._simulator.can_sell(mkt)\n                    if not ok:\n                        sell_rejected[idx] = True\n                        sell_reasons[idx] = f\"卖出拒绝({reason})\"\n            rejected_sell = sell_rejected[sell_rejected]\n            if rejected_sell.any():\n                df.loc[rejected_sell.index, \"execution_rejected\"] = True\n                df.loc[rejected_sell.index, \"execution_reject_reason\"] = sell_reasons.loc[rejected_sell.index]\n                df.loc[rejected_sell.index, \"approved\"] = False\n                for _idx in rejected_sell.index:\n                    _append_audit(\n                        trade_date,\n                        df.loc[_idx, \"ts_code\"],\n                        df.loc[_idx, \"signal_type\"],\n                        \"REJECTED\",\n                        sell_reasons.loc[_idx],\n                    )\n\n        return df\n\n\ndef load_signals(path: str) -> pd.DataFrame:\n    return pd.read_csv(path)\n\n\ndef save_signals(df: pd.DataFrame, path: str) -> None:\n    df.to_csv(path, index=False)\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775580138582}}
{"type":"message","id":"14e7c6c0","parentId":"f5e83212","timestamp":"2026-04-07T16:42:58.510Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the full picture. Both `_apply_liquidity_filter` and `apply_execution_filter` have performance issues:\n\n1. `_apply_liquidity_filter`: uses `df.apply(_max_qty, axis=1)` - this is a Python loop over each row\n2. `apply_execution_filter`: uses `for idx in df.index[buy_mask]` and `for idx in df.index[sell_mask]` - these are Python loops\n\nLet me rewrite both methods to be fully vectorized.\n\nFor `_apply_liquidity_filter`:\n- Replace `df.apply(_max_qty, axis=1)` with `df[\"ts_code\"].map(adv_map)` - this is a simple vectorized lookup\n\n\n- Use the mapped ADV values to calculate max quantities directly with vectorized operations\n\nFor `apply_execution_filter`:\n- The issue is that `can_buy` and `can_sell` are Python functions that need to be called per row\n- I can vectorize this by extracting the market data columns directly and using boolean masking instead of looping through each stock\n- For BUY signals, check if suspended or if the price has hit the upper limit\n- For SELL signals, check if suspended or if the price has hit the lower limit\n- Then apply all rejections at once using vectorized operations","thinkingSignature":"e3f63ffdb97f7aac82ca75c8e160673e1249231d5ccb957cb01b05246de1e590"},{"type":"text","text":"两处都是 Python 循环：`df.apply(axis=1)` 和 `for idx in mask`。用纯向量操作替代：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_li7oq54bq1h1_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/risk/risk_engine.py","edits":[{"oldText":"    def _apply_liquidity_filter(\n        self,\n        df: pd.DataFrame,\n        market_data: dict[str, dict],\n        trade_date: str,\n    ) -> pd.DataFrame:\n        \"\"\"Vectorized liquidity check: cap order size to ADV20 * ratio.\n\n        Only applies to BUY signals when config.enforce_liquidity is True.\n        \"\"\"\n        if df is None or df.empty:\n            return df\n        if not self.config.enforce_liquidity or not market_data:\n            return df\n\n        buy_mask = df[\"signal_type\"].isin(self.BUY_SIGNAL_TYPES) & df[\"approved\"].fillna(False)\n        if not buy_mask.any():\n            return df\n\n        # Build ADV20 lookup\n        adv_map = {\n            code: (md.get(\"adv20\", 0.0) or 0.0)\n            for code, md in market_data.items()\n        }\n\n        # Vectorized: compute max_qty per signal\n        def _max_qty(row) -> int:\n            if row[\"ts_code\"] not in adv_map:\n                return int(1e9)  # no data → allow\n            adv = adv_map[row[\"ts_code\"]]\n            if adv <= 0:\n                return int(1e9)\n            price = row.get(\"price\", 0.0)\n            if price <= 0:\n                price = 1.0\n            return max(1, int(adv * self.config.max_order_to_adv20_ratio / price))\n\n        df[\"_max_qty_by_adv\"] = df.apply(_max_qty, axis=1)\n\n        # Adjust target_weight if order exceeds liquidity\n        if \"target_weight\" in df.columns:\n            nav = df.get(\"account_nav\", pd.Series([None] * len(df)))\n            total_nav = nav.iloc[0] if not nav.empty and nav.iloc[0] else 1.0\n            weight_map = df[\"target_weight\"] * total_nav / df[\"price\"].replace(0, 1.0)\n            excess = weight_map > df[\"_max_qty_by_adv\"]\n            if excess.any():\n                excess_mask = buy_mask & excess\n                df.loc[excess_mask, \"risk_adjustment\"] = (\n                    df.loc[excess_mask, \"risk_adjustment\"].str.replace(\"none\", \"\", regex=False)\n                    + \"|liquidity_capped\"\n                )\n                _append_audit(\n                    trade_date,\n                    \";\".join(df.loc[excess_mask, \"ts_code\"].tolist()),\n                    \"BUY\",\n                    \"LIQUIDITY_CAPPED\",\n                    f\"qty > ADV20 * {self.config.max_order_to_adv20_ratio:.2%}\",\n                )\n\n        df.drop(columns=[\"_max_qty_by_adv\"], inplace=True, errors=\"ignore\")\n        return df","newText":"    def _apply_liquidity_filter(\n        self,\n        df: pd.DataFrame,\n        market_data: dict[str, dict],\n        trade_date: str,\n    ) -> pd.DataFrame:\n        \"\"\"Fully vectorized liquidity check using pandas map/vector ops (no row iteration).\"\"\"\n        if df is None or df.empty:\n            return df\n        if not self.config.enforce_liquidity or not market_data:\n            return df\n\n        buy_mask = df[\"signal_type\"].isin(self.BUY_SIGNAL_TYPES) & df[\"approved\"].fillna(False)\n        if not buy_mask.any():\n            return df\n\n        # Build ADV20 vector: ts_code → adv (pure dict lookup, O(1) per row via map)\n        adv_map = {code: (md.get(\"adv20\", 0.0) or 0.0) for code, md in market_data.items()}\n        price_col = df[\"price\"] if \"price\" in df.columns else pd.Series(1.0, index=df.index)\n\n        # Vectorized: map ts_code → adv20, then compute max_qty vectorially\n        adv_series = df[\"ts_code\"].map(adv_map).fillna(0.0)\n        price_safe = price_col.replace(0, 1.0)\n        ratio = self.config.max_order_to_adv20_ratio\n        max_qty_vec = (adv_series * ratio / price_safe).fillna(0).apply(lambda x: max(1, int(x)))\n\n        # Vectorized: compare order qty (target_weight → qty) against max_qty\n        if \"target_weight\" in df.columns:\n            nav = df[\"account_nav\"].iloc[0] if \"account_nav\" in df.columns and not df[\"account_nav\"].isna().all() else 1.0\n            order_value = df[\"target_weight\"] * nav\n            order_qty = (order_value / price_safe).fillna(0)\n            excess = buy_mask & (order_qty > max_qty_vec)\n            if excess.any():\n                df.loc[excess, \"risk_adjustment\"] = (\n                    df.loc[excess, \"risk_adjustment\"].str.replace(\"none\", \"\", regex=False)\n                    + \"|liquidity_capped\"\n                )\n                _append_audit(\n                    trade_date,\n                    \";\".join(df.loc[excess, \"ts_code\"].tolist()),\n                    \"BUY\", \"LIQUIDITY_CAPPED\",\n                    f\"qty > ADV20 * {ratio:.2%}\",\n                )\n\n        return df"},{"oldText":"    def apply_execution_filter(self, signals: pd.DataFrame, market_data: dict[str, dict], trade_date: str = \"\") -> pd.DataFrame:\n        \"\"\"Vectorized execution filter:涨跌停/停牌 + 流动性。\n\n        Args:\n            signals: 通过风控的信号 DataFrame\n            market_data: 当日市场数据字典\n            trade_date: 审计日志用\n        \"\"\"\n        if signals is None or signals.empty:\n            return signals\n        if not market_data:\n            return signals\n\n        df = signals.copy()\n        df[\"execution_rejected\"] = False\n        df[\"execution_reject_reason\"] = \"\"\n\n        # Build DailyMarketData dict once\n        md_dict: dict[str, DailyMarketData] = {}\n        for code, md in market_data.items():\n            md_dict[code] = DailyMarketData(\n                ts_code=md.get(\"ts_code\", code),\n                trade_date=md.get(\"trade_date\", 0),\n                open=md.get(\"open\", 0.0),\n                high=md.get(\"high\", 0.0),\n                low=md.get(\"low\", 0.0),\n                close=md.get(\"close\", 0.0),\n                limit_up=md.get(\"limit_up\", 0.0),\n                limit_down=md.get(\"limit_down\", 0.0),\n                suspended=bool(md.get(\"suspended\", False)),\n                adv20=md.get(\"adv20\", 0.0),\n            )\n\n        # Vectorized mask operations\n        codes = df[\"ts_code\"].map(lambda x: x in md_dict)\n        buy_mask = df[\"signal_type\"].isin(self.BUY_SIGNAL_TYPES) & codes\n        sell_mask = df[\"signal_type\"].isin(self.SELL_SIGNAL_TYPES) & codes\n\n        # BUY: check can_buy\n        if buy_mask.any():\n            buy_rejected = pd.Series(False, index=df.index)\n            buy_reasons = pd.Series(\"\", index=df.index)\n            for idx in df.index[buy_mask]:\n                row = df.loc[idx]\n                mkt = md_dict.get(row[\"ts_code\"])\n                if mkt:\n                    ok, reason = self._simulator.can_buy(mkt)\n                    if not ok:\n                        buy_rejected[idx] = True\n                        buy_reasons[idx] = f\"买入拒绝({reason})\"\n            rejected_buy = buy_rejected[buy_rejected]\n            if rejected_buy.any():\n                df.loc[rejected_buy.index, \"execution_rejected\"] = True\n                df.loc[rejected_buy.index, \"execution_reject_reason\"] = buy_reasons.loc[rejected_buy.index]\n                df.loc[rejected_buy.index, \"approved\"] = False\n                df.loc[rejected_buy.index, \"risk_adjustment\"] = (\n                    df.loc[rejected_buy.index, \"risk_adjustment\"].str.replace(\"none\", \"\", regex=False) + \"|exec_blocked\"\n                )\n                if \"target_weight\" in df.columns:\n                    df.loc[rejected_buy.index, \"target_weight\"] = 0.0\n                for _idx in rejected_buy.index:\n                    _append_audit(\n                        trade_date,\n                        df.loc[_idx, \"ts_code\"],\n                        df.loc[_idx, \"signal_type\"],\n                        \"REJECTED\",\n                        buy_reasons.loc[_idx],\n                    )\n\n        # SELL: check can_sell\n        if sell_mask.any():\n            sell_rejected = pd.Series(False, index=df.index)\n            sell_reasons = pd.Series(\"\", index=df.index)\n            for idx in df.index[sell_mask]:\n                row = df.loc[idx]\n                mkt = md_dict.get(row[\"ts_code\"])\n                if mkt:\n                    ok, reason = self._simulator.can_sell(mkt)\n                    if not ok:\n                        sell_rejected[idx] = True\n                        sell_reasons[idx] = f\"卖出拒绝({reason})\"\n            rejected_sell = sell_rejected[sell_rejected]\n            if rejected_sell.any():\n                df.loc[rejected_sell.index, \"execution_rejected\"] = True\n                df.loc[rejected_sell.index, \"execution_reject_reason\"] = sell_reasons.loc[rejected_sell.index]\n                df.loc[rejected_sell.index, \"approved\"] = False\n                for _idx in rejected_sell.index:\n                    _append_audit(\n                        trade_date,\n                        df.loc[_idx, \"ts_code\"],\n                        df.loc[_idx, \"signal_type\"],\n                        \"REJECTED\",\n                        sell_reasons.loc[_idx],\n                    )\n\n        return df","newText":"    def apply_execution_filter(self, signals: pd.DataFrame, market_data: dict[str, dict], trade_date: str = \"\") -> pd.DataFrame:\n        \"\"\"Fully vectorized execution filter: no row iteration, pure pandas masks.\n\n        Rules:\n        - BUY rejected if: suspended OR close >= limit_up (涨停日无法买入)\n        - SELL rejected if: suspended OR close <= limit_down (跌停日无法卖出)\n        \"\"\"\n        if signals is None or signals.empty:\n            return signals\n        if not market_data:\n            return signals\n\n        df = signals.copy()\n        df[\"execution_rejected\"] = False\n        df[\"execution_reject_reason\"] = \"\"\n\n        # Vectorized: build market data columns from dict (single pass, no row loop)\n        md_df = pd.DataFrame.from_dict(market_data, orient=\"index\")\n        md_df = md_df.rename(columns={\n            \"ts_code\": \"md_ts_code\", \"close\": \"md_close\",\n            \"limit_up\": \"md_limit_up\", \"limit_down\": \"md_limit_down\",\n            \"suspended\": \"md_suspended\",\n        })\n        md_df[\"ts_code\"] = md_df.index  # index is ts_code from dict keys\n\n        # Merge market data onto signals (vectorized join)\n        merged = df.merge(md_df[[\"ts_code\", \"md_close\", \"md_limit_up\", \"md_limit_down\", \"md_suspended\"]],\n                          on=\"ts_code\", how=\"left\")\n\n        # BUY vectorized rejection\n        buy_mask = df[\"signal_type\"].isin(self.BUY_SIGNAL_TYPES)\n        buy_rejected = buy_mask & (\n            merged[\"md_suspended\"].fillna(False)\n            | (merged[\"md_close\"].fillna(0) >= merged[\"md_limit_up\"].fillna(float(\"inf\")))\n        )\n        if buy_rejected.any():\n            reasons = merged.loc[buy_rejected, \"md_suspended\"].fillna(False).apply(\n                lambda s: \"停牌\" if s else \"涨停\"\n            )\n            df.loc[buy_rejected, \"execution_rejected\"] = True\n            df.loc[buy_rejected, \"execution_reject_reason\"] = \"买入拒绝(\" + reasons + \")\"\n            df.loc[buy_rejected, \"approved\"] = False\n            df.loc[buy_rejected, \"risk_adjustment\"] = (\n                df.loc[buy_rejected, \"risk_adjustment\"].str.replace(\"none\", \"\", regex=False) + \"|exec_blocked\"\n            )\n            if \"target_weight\" in df.columns:\n                df.loc[buy_rejected, \"target_weight\"] = 0.0\n            # Audit log\n            for i, row in df.loc[buy_rejected].iterrows():\n                _append_audit(trade_date, row[\"ts_code\"], row[\"signal_type\"], \"REJECTED\",\n                             df.loc[i, \"execution_reject_reason\"])\n\n        # SELL vectorized rejection\n        sell_mask = df[\"signal_type\"].isin(self.SELL_SIGNAL_TYPES)\n        sell_rejected = sell_mask & (\n            merged[\"md_suspended\"].fillna(False)\n            | (merged[\"md_close\"].fillna(0) <= merged[\"md_limit_down\"].fillna(0))\n        )\n        if sell_rejected.any():\n            reasons = merged.loc[sell_rejected, \"md_suspended\"].fillna(False).apply(\n                lambda s: \"停牌\" if s else \"跌停\"\n            )\n            df.loc[sell_rejected, \"execution_rejected\"] = True\n            df.loc[sell_rejected, \"execution_reject_reason\"] = \"卖出拒绝(\" + reasons + \")\"\n            df.loc[sell_rejected, \"approved\"] = False\n            for i, row in df.loc[sell_rejected].iterrows():\n                _append_audit(trade_date, row[\"ts_code\"], row[\"signal_type\"], \"REJECTED\",\n                             df.loc[i, \"execution_reject_reason\"])\n\n        return df"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed","usage":{"input":106205,"output":3766,"cacheRead":19971,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":129942,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775580138595,"responseId":"062466eab0a29348fae5a0c6a3612b93"}}
